1
00:01:32,469 --> 00:01:36,945
(Zhan Zhao Adventures)

2
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:39,964
(Episode 20)

3
00:01:40,563 --> 00:01:41,808
Did Uncle die of illness?

4
00:01:42,203 --> 00:01:44,705
How come no one in the martial world ever mentioned it?

5
00:01:45,123 --> 00:01:46,123
Illness?

6
00:01:47,963 --> 00:01:49,608
He wasn't that lucky.

7
00:01:50,843 --> 00:01:52,819
Life in the martial world is full of fighting and killing.

8
00:01:52,843 --> 00:01:54,380
You are always living on edge.

9
00:01:54,883 --> 00:01:56,528
One day, you take someone's life,

10
00:01:56,763 --> 00:01:59,609
the next day, someone else will come for yours.

11
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,567
My uncle was murdered?

12
00:02:02,042 --> 00:02:03,065
I don't know.

13
00:02:03,802 --> 00:02:05,025
Some time ago,

14
00:02:05,403 --> 00:02:07,169
Shengyun Manor was attacked.

15
00:02:08,202 --> 00:02:10,248
Several skilled fighters entered the manor

16
00:02:10,362 --> 00:02:11,562
and went on a killing spree.

17
00:02:11,642 --> 00:02:12,665
They captured him.

18
00:02:13,523 --> 00:02:16,026
And no one has heard from him since.

19
00:02:16,523 --> 00:02:19,288
When my son Si Yuan and his men found the body,

20
00:02:20,322 --> 00:02:22,499
it had been lying out in the open in a ravine for several days.

21
00:02:22,523 --> 00:02:24,129
Did they find out who the killer was?

22
00:02:24,442 --> 00:02:26,369
Si Yuan didn't want me to worry.

23
00:02:27,082 --> 00:02:28,265
He only said

24
00:02:28,843 --> 00:02:30,928
that he had a revenge plan in mind.

25
00:02:32,722 --> 00:02:34,369
But I'm worried about him.

26
00:02:34,722 --> 00:02:37,562
Seeking revenge will only bring more killing and put him in harm's way.

27
00:02:39,163 --> 00:02:40,265
Enough of that.

28
00:02:40,883 --> 00:02:41,883
Please, sit.

29
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:50,647
I just saw you coming out from the yard next door.

30
00:02:51,363 --> 00:02:52,688
What were you doing there?

31
00:02:52,842 --> 00:02:54,283
That's my friend's old house.

32
00:02:54,430 --> 00:02:55,670
We were handling some business.

33
00:02:57,762 --> 00:03:00,248
If you don't have a place to stay,

34
00:03:00,762 --> 00:03:02,705
why don't you move in with me?

35
00:03:03,643 --> 00:03:05,888
No, thank you. I appreciate your concern, Aunt.

36
00:03:15,163 --> 00:03:17,163
He said Cuixi Forest in the back mountains, right?

37
00:03:17,402 --> 00:03:18,402
Yes.

38
00:03:18,643 --> 00:03:19,866
I heard correctly.

39
00:03:20,803 --> 00:03:21,803
Master!

40
00:03:22,443 --> 00:03:24,625
Master, you need to come quickly!

41
00:03:25,202 --> 00:03:28,328
Master, there's a huge commotion at Qinghui Hall!

42
00:03:28,643 --> 00:03:31,809
Jin Xue Wen... He's returned and signed up for the Suwen Tournament!

43
00:03:32,762 --> 00:03:33,762
What?

44
00:03:33,963 --> 00:03:35,803
When Steward Xu saw the name on the roster,

45
00:03:35,883 --> 00:03:37,083
his face darkened.

46
00:03:37,163 --> 00:03:39,683
He started arguing with the visitor, and the quarrel escalated.

47
00:03:39,749 --> 00:03:42,395
Now, a crowd had gathered around Qinghui Hall.

48
00:03:43,083 --> 00:03:45,163
Oh no, I've been tricked.

49
00:03:47,243 --> 00:03:49,406
He says his name is Jin Xue Wen,

50
00:03:49,682 --> 00:03:51,529
the ninth young master of the Jin family.

51
00:03:51,803 --> 00:03:55,363
Strange. I've never heard of anyone by that name in the Jin family.

52
00:03:55,562 --> 00:03:57,522
- Neither have I. - Right?

53
00:03:57,602 --> 00:04:01,943
You're too young to know that case. There was such a person.

54
00:04:02,083 --> 00:04:04,400
He committed a crime years ago and died in prison.

55
00:04:04,842 --> 00:04:07,098
- He died in prison? - He's been dead for over ten years.

56
00:04:07,122 --> 00:04:08,409
What? Dead?

57
00:04:09,083 --> 00:04:10,378
Then who's the one kneeling there?

58
00:04:10,402 --> 00:04:11,522
I remember now.

59
00:04:11,602 --> 00:04:14,363
My grandfather told me a long time ago that this case was suspicious.

60
00:04:14,562 --> 00:04:16,808
Jin Xue Wen was probably wronged.

61
00:04:17,243 --> 00:04:19,482
I heard that the case wasn't even concluded back then.

62
00:04:19,562 --> 00:04:21,019
But the Jin family did nothing to help.

63
00:04:21,043 --> 00:04:23,883
That's how that ninth young master ended up dying of illness in prison.

64
00:04:24,323 --> 00:04:25,522
Is that true?

65
00:04:25,602 --> 00:04:26,602
Yeah.

66
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:31,200
I've always said it, these big wealthy families are no good.

67
00:04:31,402 --> 00:04:33,682
- Exactly. - That's right. Nothing good.

68
00:04:34,243 --> 00:04:35,899
Why hasn't the head of the Jin family shown up?

69
00:04:35,923 --> 00:04:37,328
Is he hiding?

70
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,845
Is the Jin family feeling guilty?

71
00:04:40,243 --> 00:04:42,922
I heard that as soon as the name Jin Xue Wen was written down,

72
00:04:43,002 --> 00:04:44,608
the old steward nearly passed out.

73
00:04:45,923 --> 00:04:46,923
Nonsense!

74
00:04:47,763 --> 00:04:49,400
I'm going to smash that mouth of yours!

75
00:04:50,923 --> 00:04:52,169
Old man.

76
00:04:54,602 --> 00:04:56,802
At your age, you really shouldn't be running like that.

77
00:04:56,882 --> 00:04:58,082
Slow down.

78
00:04:58,162 --> 00:04:59,162
Let go!

79
00:04:59,602 --> 00:05:01,048
You think I don't see it?

80
00:05:02,363 --> 00:05:03,849
You're all in cahoots!

81
00:05:04,722 --> 00:05:05,746
Move! Move!

82
00:05:12,483 --> 00:05:13,483
Third,

83
00:05:14,002 --> 00:05:16,123
that debt collector has come back!

84
00:05:16,203 --> 00:05:17,203
Mr. Xu.

85
00:05:18,043 --> 00:05:19,648
Since you know who he is,

86
00:05:20,043 --> 00:05:23,048
why waste words arguing with him in front of outsiders?

87
00:05:24,803 --> 00:05:26,443
Everyone who has no business here, leave.

88
00:05:26,882 --> 00:05:30,402
Break it up, break it up! Everyone out!

89
00:05:32,363 --> 00:05:33,363
Out!

90
00:05:34,108 --> 00:05:36,149
Are you leaving or not? Out!

91
00:05:36,562 --> 00:05:38,720
- This tree is pretty. - It really is.

92
00:05:38,803 --> 00:05:39,803
Out!

93
00:05:41,682 --> 00:05:43,363
- Third... - Mr. Xu.

94
00:05:43,923 --> 00:05:44,945
Leave us.

95
00:06:05,683 --> 00:06:08,248
Becoming the head of the family really changes a person.

96
00:06:09,282 --> 00:06:10,688
Quite the airs you put on now.

97
00:06:11,402 --> 00:06:14,563
I remember back then, you wouldn't dare boss people around in the house.

98
00:06:14,643 --> 00:06:16,488
You used to act so gentle and refined.

99
00:06:17,123 --> 00:06:19,402
What's the matter? Done pretending?

100
00:06:19,883 --> 00:06:21,248
So it really is you.

101
00:06:22,123 --> 00:06:23,145
Little Seventeenth.

102
00:06:24,282 --> 00:06:25,385
You're alive.

103
00:06:26,802 --> 00:06:28,048
Sounds like

104
00:06:28,402 --> 00:06:31,329
you even sent people to look for me after the shipwreck.

105
00:06:31,963 --> 00:06:33,683
You were afraid I hadn't died, weren't you?

106
00:06:34,643 --> 00:06:36,769
You've been gone for years.

107
00:06:37,523 --> 00:06:40,124
The moment you came back, you kidnapped the descendants of our family

108
00:06:40,148 --> 00:06:42,228
and forced me to use our family's precious treasure.

109
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,401
How vicious.

110
00:06:44,496 --> 00:06:45,981
Not as vicious as you.

111
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,207
Outwardly saving people,

112
00:06:51,422 --> 00:06:53,622
but secretly colluding with the Tang Sect to harm them.

113
00:06:54,083 --> 00:06:55,849
Head of the Jin family, how capable.

114
00:06:58,402 --> 00:07:00,625
Relax. I have no proof.

115
00:07:01,003 --> 00:07:02,329
Just wanted to scare you.

116
00:07:02,602 --> 00:07:05,568
You caused such a huge commotion as soon as you returned.

117
00:07:06,963 --> 00:07:08,025
What do you want?

118
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,023
Didn't anyone tell you what I wanted?

119
00:07:10,643 --> 00:07:12,688
I'm here for the Suwen Tournament, of course.

120
00:07:17,242 --> 00:07:18,889
You left home when you were ten.

121
00:07:19,123 --> 00:07:21,563
Your medical skills have long been neglected.

122
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:24,120
What makes you think you can compete in the Suwen Tournament?

123
00:07:24,362 --> 00:07:25,969
It's true I've neglected them.

124
00:07:26,402 --> 00:07:27,883
But I'll only be embarrassing myself.

125
00:07:27,963 --> 00:07:29,202
What's it to you?

126
00:07:29,282 --> 00:07:31,089
You're using his name.

127
00:07:31,842 --> 00:07:33,769
You're using Jin family's name.

128
00:07:36,203 --> 00:07:39,282
You came here on purpose to embarrass us, didn't you?

129
00:07:39,683 --> 00:07:40,683
Yes.

130
00:07:40,802 --> 00:07:44,409
I came precisely to embarrass Jin family and make things hard for you.

131
00:07:48,722 --> 00:07:51,202
So either I embarrass the Jin family at the Suwen Tournament,

132
00:07:51,282 --> 00:07:54,010
or you hand over the antidote to Nightmare Sky.

133
00:07:54,182 --> 00:07:55,366
Your choice.

134
00:07:57,282 --> 00:07:58,282
Nightmare Sky?

135
00:07:59,042 --> 00:08:00,145
What are you talking about?

136
00:08:00,763 --> 00:08:02,048
I've never even heard of it.

137
00:08:02,362 --> 00:08:03,465
Stop pretending.

138
00:08:03,922 --> 00:08:06,910
I'm asking you to hand over the antidote, not to make it.

139
00:08:07,242 --> 00:08:08,649
Guess why I said that.

140
00:08:13,203 --> 00:08:14,203
Zhan Zhao.

141
00:08:16,083 --> 00:08:17,329
Come out, Zhan Zhao.

142
00:08:18,123 --> 00:08:21,209
Zhan Zhao must have put you up to this.

143
00:08:21,922 --> 00:08:22,922
Am I right?

144
00:08:23,763 --> 00:08:25,089
I even saved his life once.

145
00:08:25,683 --> 00:08:27,289
And this is how he repays me.

146
00:08:30,003 --> 00:08:31,683
I came here on my own.

147
00:08:31,763 --> 00:08:33,338
What does this have to do with Zhan Zhao?

148
00:08:33,362 --> 00:08:35,523
And stop saying you saved his life.

149
00:08:35,802 --> 00:08:36,945
I'm certain

150
00:08:37,362 --> 00:08:40,649
the one who used Naiheyin to save Zhan Zhao wasn't you, but Fourth Aunt.

151
00:08:41,242 --> 00:08:42,969
So stop taking credit for it.

152
00:08:43,203 --> 00:08:44,842
Zhan Zhao is courteous and proper.

153
00:08:44,922 --> 00:08:48,079
He's brought gifts to visit my Fourth Aunt.

154
00:08:48,222 --> 00:08:50,027
You can't rebuke him.

155
00:08:53,162 --> 00:08:54,162
Oh, Third,

156
00:08:54,643 --> 00:08:56,008
you really aren't very bright.

157
00:08:56,922 --> 00:09:00,488
You've fallen for the diversion tactic twice.

158
00:09:17,963 --> 00:09:19,368
Little Seventeenth.

159
00:09:21,842 --> 00:09:22,842
Fourth Aunt.

160
00:09:27,242 --> 00:09:28,688
Little Seventeenth.

161
00:09:29,602 --> 00:09:32,643
When Zhan Zhao told me about you earlier, I didn't believe him.

162
00:09:34,123 --> 00:09:36,008
I thought you had died

163
00:09:38,282 --> 00:09:39,529
15 years ago.

164
00:09:42,162 --> 00:09:43,346
It's all in the past now.

165
00:09:44,162 --> 00:09:45,162
See?

166
00:09:45,643 --> 00:09:46,643
Strong and healthy.

167
00:09:47,963 --> 00:09:48,963
Yes.

168
00:09:49,722 --> 00:09:51,248
You've grown so much.

169
00:09:51,563 --> 00:09:53,128
Heaven finally showed some mercy

170
00:09:53,842 --> 00:09:55,729
and spared a poor child like you.

171
00:09:56,922 --> 00:09:59,522
Don't just stand out here. Come inside with me.

172
00:09:59,602 --> 00:10:00,602
Alright.

173
00:10:01,213 --> 00:10:02,242
Wait.

174
00:10:03,162 --> 00:10:04,346
You can't leave yet.

175
00:10:11,083 --> 00:10:13,369
You were so busy trying to save the Jin family's face

176
00:10:13,842 --> 00:10:16,202
that you forgot to ask why I was kneeling here, didn't you?

177
00:10:16,803 --> 00:10:18,156
My reasons for coming back this time are,

178
00:10:18,180 --> 00:10:20,580
first, to reclaim my identity as a member of the Jin family;

179
00:10:20,683 --> 00:10:23,226
and second, to apologize to Fifth Granduncle

180
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,120
for kidnapping the Jin family descendants.

181
00:10:26,043 --> 00:10:27,225
I knew

182
00:10:27,443 --> 00:10:29,698
that you would keep the matter of Naiheyin Pill being used up

183
00:10:29,722 --> 00:10:31,009
completely under wraps;

184
00:10:31,283 --> 00:10:33,963
otherwise, you'd lose too much face as the head of the Jin family.

185
00:10:34,568 --> 00:10:36,192
Fifth Granduncle already knows about it.

186
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:40,079
He ordered you to kneel here for two hours before going to see him.

187
00:10:44,443 --> 00:10:45,443
Fourth Aunt,

188
00:10:46,002 --> 00:10:47,482
Fifth Granduncle is being quite fair.

189
00:10:47,842 --> 00:10:49,360
I've received my punishment,

190
00:10:49,522 --> 00:10:51,289
so naturally, he should accept his too.

191
00:10:52,602 --> 00:10:53,602
Come on.

192
00:11:00,323 --> 00:11:03,928
That old steward earlier was probably trying to remind you about this.

193
00:11:04,882 --> 00:11:05,882
Too bad

194
00:11:06,283 --> 00:11:08,009
you didn't let him finish.

195
00:11:10,683 --> 00:11:12,289
You've got terrible luck.

196
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,600
It's about to rain.

197
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:27,000
(15 years ago)

198
00:11:42,522 --> 00:11:43,626
Stop kneeling.

199
00:11:44,122 --> 00:11:45,442
You've done everything you could.

200
00:11:47,403 --> 00:11:48,728
You're still just a child.

201
00:11:50,443 --> 00:11:51,626
This is really hard on you.

202
00:11:53,122 --> 00:11:54,649
If my brother dies,

203
00:11:55,283 --> 00:11:56,609
I won't have a home anymore.

204
00:12:01,722 --> 00:12:03,249
As long as I'm here,

205
00:12:04,323 --> 00:12:05,609
this is your home.

206
00:12:07,923 --> 00:12:08,923
Come.

207
00:12:14,403 --> 00:12:15,465
In the entire Jin family,

208
00:12:15,762 --> 00:12:17,962
you're the only one who has ever truly been kind to me.

209
00:12:18,043 --> 00:12:20,163
I still remember everything from before.

210
00:12:20,443 --> 00:12:22,208
After the shipwreck back then,

211
00:12:22,443 --> 00:12:24,163
Jin family did send people to look for you.

212
00:12:24,588 --> 00:12:25,731
They said you...

213
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:30,443
It's all Jin family's fault for not searching for you again,

214
00:12:30,524 --> 00:12:32,370
leaving you to fend for yourself out there.

215
00:12:33,522 --> 00:12:36,048
All these years, you must have suffered so much.

216
00:12:36,762 --> 00:12:37,762
It's fine.

217
00:12:38,122 --> 00:12:40,506
I roamed the martial world and learned plenty of skills.

218
00:12:42,403 --> 00:12:43,403
Fourth Aunt,

219
00:12:43,842 --> 00:12:46,522
I came back this time because I need something from the Jin family.

220
00:12:48,683 --> 00:12:50,323
Zhan Zhao has told me about it.

221
00:12:50,404 --> 00:12:52,681
The poison those people were given is called

222
00:12:53,003 --> 00:12:54,041
Nightmare Sky.

223
00:12:54,122 --> 00:12:55,345
Have you heard of this poison?

224
00:12:56,563 --> 00:12:57,563
Well...

225
00:12:59,403 --> 00:13:00,848
Perhaps I have.

226
00:13:02,163 --> 00:13:03,409
I can't quite remember.

227
00:13:04,283 --> 00:13:05,529
I'm really not sure.

228
00:13:07,242 --> 00:13:09,585
The way things got so tense between you and Third earlier,

229
00:13:10,163 --> 00:13:11,489
was it also about this?

230
00:13:13,443 --> 00:13:15,529
Although Third's medical skills are exceptional,

231
00:13:15,803 --> 00:13:17,609
he's not some immortal healer.

232
00:13:17,803 --> 00:13:19,649
There are times when even he can do nothing.

233
00:13:20,563 --> 00:13:21,786
If he's refusing to help,

234
00:13:22,043 --> 00:13:24,169
perhaps it really is beyond his abilities.

235
00:13:24,563 --> 00:13:25,563
No.

236
00:13:25,722 --> 00:13:27,249
He can definitely cure this poison.

237
00:13:27,882 --> 00:13:29,208
Why are you so certain?

238
00:13:38,323 --> 00:13:41,026
I can't go into the details of why.

239
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,659
But I urgently need the antidote to save people.

240
00:13:43,683 --> 00:13:45,043
Please, try to think of something.

241
00:13:50,323 --> 00:13:51,848
I'm just a woman.

242
00:13:52,803 --> 00:13:54,649
I'm afraid I can't be of much help.

243
00:13:55,882 --> 00:13:57,409
I'll try to talk to Third again.

244
00:13:58,283 --> 00:13:59,529
As for the Nightmare Sky,

245
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,686
let me have a look at it.

246
00:14:02,203 --> 00:14:04,369
I did come from a family of physicians, after all.

247
00:14:05,722 --> 00:14:06,722
Fourth Aunt...

248
00:14:07,403 --> 00:14:08,465
It's getting late.

249
00:14:09,203 --> 00:14:10,923
I'll go tell the kitchen to prepare dinner.

250
00:14:11,203 --> 00:14:13,289
You should stay and eat here tonight.

251
00:14:13,968 --> 00:14:14,968
Fourth Aunt,

252
00:14:15,602 --> 00:14:17,042
I want to stay at the Jin Residence.

253
00:14:21,362 --> 00:14:22,362
Of course.

254
00:14:22,722 --> 00:14:24,985
Since you've come back, stay a few more days.

255
00:14:26,722 --> 00:14:28,728
This used to be your Fourth Uncle's study.

256
00:14:29,043 --> 00:14:31,465
After he passed away, it's been empty.

257
00:14:32,122 --> 00:14:34,328
I still have the say over this room.

258
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,807
You can stay here without worry.

259
00:14:48,362 --> 00:14:50,643
Let them pretend to be your attendants and stay with you.

260
00:14:51,522 --> 00:14:53,968
They've got some quick wits.

261
00:14:54,522 --> 00:14:55,842
Tonight, let them feel things out

262
00:14:56,882 --> 00:14:58,242
and gather some information first.

263
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:22,840
(Fifth Granduncle, Elder Clan Leader of the Jin Family)

264
00:15:25,362 --> 00:15:26,362
Come in.

265
00:15:31,923 --> 00:15:32,923
Third,

266
00:15:34,803 --> 00:15:35,803
get up.

267
00:15:57,963 --> 00:15:58,963
Fifth Granduncle.

268
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:02,840
You used Naiheyin Pill to save someone's life.

269
00:16:03,002 --> 00:16:04,082
I don't blame you for that.

270
00:16:05,203 --> 00:16:07,603
But hiding it from me

271
00:16:07,683 --> 00:16:09,568
and keeping the clan elders in the dark,

272
00:16:09,842 --> 00:16:10,842
that deserves punishment.

273
00:16:11,443 --> 00:16:12,443
I accept the punishment.

274
00:16:13,482 --> 00:16:15,922
Little Seventeenth said that you colluded with the Tang Sect.

275
00:16:16,522 --> 00:16:18,282
Do you have anything to say in your defense?

276
00:16:21,002 --> 00:16:22,146
Tang Sect?

277
00:16:23,043 --> 00:16:24,723
He's just spouting nonsense!

278
00:16:24,803 --> 00:16:26,649
Can't you see?

279
00:16:27,283 --> 00:16:28,386
He came back this time

280
00:16:28,923 --> 00:16:31,546
with the sole intention of getting revenge on us.

281
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,183
After all was said and done,

282
00:16:37,842 --> 00:16:41,489
we didn't really put in the effort to find him after the shipwreck.

283
00:16:42,203 --> 00:16:43,386
It's only natural

284
00:16:44,683 --> 00:16:45,968
for him to hold resentment.

285
00:16:46,362 --> 00:16:49,745
If he merely resents me for abandoning him out there,

286
00:16:50,642 --> 00:16:52,649
I'm willing to apologize and make amends.

287
00:16:53,163 --> 00:16:55,373
But he's clearly making baseless accusations,

288
00:16:55,602 --> 00:16:56,842
slandering me without evidence.

289
00:16:57,002 --> 00:16:59,282
And those people with him, none of them are good.

290
00:16:59,362 --> 00:17:00,465
They're all in cahoots.

291
00:17:00,762 --> 00:17:02,243
They won't stop hounding me.

292
00:17:02,323 --> 00:17:04,208
Why would they hound you like that?

293
00:17:04,683 --> 00:17:05,683
Third,

294
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:09,443
could it be you really did something bad after all?

295
00:17:14,242 --> 00:17:15,242
Fifth Granduncle,

296
00:17:16,755 --> 00:17:18,291
I've spent my entire life healing and saving people.

297
00:17:18,315 --> 00:17:19,912
How could I possibly do something bad?

298
00:17:20,803 --> 00:17:23,283
If you'd rather believe outsiders than me,

299
00:17:24,803 --> 00:17:26,369
then there's nothing more I can say.

300
00:17:27,482 --> 00:17:29,923
Thank you both for inviting us for drinks.

301
00:17:30,203 --> 00:17:32,620
Come on, don't be shy. We just like making friends.

302
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:34,803
Bottoms up! Have some more!

303
00:17:38,602 --> 00:17:40,218
A little more. It's good stuff. Drink up.

304
00:17:40,242 --> 00:17:41,786
Here, some more.

305
00:18:02,563 --> 00:18:05,728
Look at all of you, drunk and red-faced!

306
00:18:07,122 --> 00:18:08,489
Just a few cups of wine in,

307
00:18:08,842 --> 00:18:10,402
and you're already running your mouths.

308
00:18:10,602 --> 00:18:13,328
Do you not want to keep your jobs here?

309
00:18:13,683 --> 00:18:16,409
I want all of you out of the estate tomorrow!

310
00:18:16,722 --> 00:18:17,722
Get out of here!

311
00:18:25,522 --> 00:18:27,448
You two little rascals,

312
00:18:28,163 --> 00:18:30,083
why are you still here?

313
00:18:30,163 --> 00:18:32,162
Fourth Madam invited us to stay for dinner.

314
00:18:32,242 --> 00:18:34,683
Yes, she even asked Bai to stay overnight.

315
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:38,680
Old man, don't just stand there. Come join us.

316
00:18:38,762 --> 00:18:41,298
You've chased everyone off, but there's still so much food left.

317
00:18:41,322 --> 00:18:43,086
Come sit with us. Don't be shy.

318
00:18:53,802 --> 00:18:55,288
What's got you so happy?

319
00:18:55,802 --> 00:18:57,129
We got some information.

320
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,176
The servants said that Jin Zhen Ping has a habit

321
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:01,016
of writing down antidote formulas and keeping them.

322
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,920
But Jin Zhen Ping and the old steward showed up

323
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,819
before we could get them to tell us where he hid them.

324
00:19:04,843 --> 00:19:06,300
Who is that old guy?

325
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,681
Dressed like a servant,

326
00:19:07,843 --> 00:19:09,569
but he acts like he owns the place.

327
00:19:09,722 --> 00:19:12,191
As soon as he started talking, everyone at the table scattered.

328
00:19:12,215 --> 00:19:14,215
Xu An has served the family for three generations.

329
00:19:14,256 --> 00:19:16,056
Even Jin Zhen Ping has to address him respectfully.

330
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:17,280
Who would dare cross him?

331
00:19:17,362 --> 00:19:18,506
We would.

332
00:19:18,642 --> 00:19:19,923
White Rat, don't worry.

333
00:19:20,123 --> 00:19:22,083
Leave the antidote to us.

334
00:19:22,163 --> 00:19:23,163
We'll find it for you.

335
00:19:23,403 --> 00:19:24,403
Alright.

336
00:19:25,002 --> 00:19:27,448
We'll go to Huaihua Alley again tomorrow.

337
00:19:32,643 --> 00:19:34,569
This is where that girl was killed.

338
00:19:35,403 --> 00:19:38,248
Did you ever come here after your brother was arrested?

339
00:19:40,963 --> 00:19:41,963
No.

340
00:19:43,762 --> 00:19:45,288
You were only ten back then.

341
00:19:45,843 --> 00:19:47,563
I suppose you were too scared to go inside.

342
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:49,640
From the arraignment to the verdict,

343
00:19:49,762 --> 00:19:51,282
Xiang Cai was in charge of everything.

344
00:19:51,443 --> 00:19:53,282
So there's a lot I don't know.

345
00:19:53,363 --> 00:19:56,089
Do you remember what happened around the time of the murder?

346
00:19:56,722 --> 00:19:59,322
What evidence did the county office use to arrest your brother?

347
00:19:59,762 --> 00:20:01,448
I remember the day before the murder,

348
00:20:01,802 --> 00:20:04,018
Xiang Cai took me to the neighboring county to visit relatives.

349
00:20:04,042 --> 00:20:05,738
We didn't get home until noon the next day.

350
00:20:05,762 --> 00:20:08,562
As soon as we arrived, I heard that someone next door had been killed.

351
00:20:09,163 --> 00:20:10,163
Step back.

352
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:12,240
Step back.

353
00:20:12,643 --> 00:20:13,843
What's going on here?

354
00:20:13,923 --> 00:20:15,465
Why are there so many officers here?

355
00:20:15,802 --> 00:20:16,945
Someone's dead.

356
00:20:17,403 --> 00:20:19,803
That girl who lives in this courtyard was killed last night.

357
00:20:20,123 --> 00:20:21,146
Died horribly.

358
00:20:21,843 --> 00:20:23,643
Move aside, let me through.

359
00:20:32,203 --> 00:20:34,505
Children aren't supposed to look at dead bodies.

360
00:20:34,755 --> 00:20:35,778
Bad luck.

361
00:20:36,363 --> 00:20:38,403
Fourth Uncle already let me watch autopsies before.

362
00:20:38,683 --> 00:20:41,442
He even taught me to identify human organs. I'm not afraid.

363
00:20:41,522 --> 00:20:44,163
If only your brother had half your drive.

364
00:20:45,082 --> 00:20:46,563
The sun's already high in the sky,

365
00:20:46,643 --> 00:20:47,643
and he's still not up.

366
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:50,200
He must have been drinking again last night.

367
00:20:50,802 --> 00:20:53,106
The Suwen Tournament is just a few days away.

368
00:20:53,443 --> 00:20:55,419
Instead of reviewing his medical texts and formulas,

369
00:20:55,443 --> 00:20:56,728
all he does is fool around.

370
00:21:33,923 --> 00:21:37,203
You're still in bed? Get up.

371
00:21:38,203 --> 00:21:41,123
What happened to you? Why are you so filthy? Hurry and clean yourself up.

372
00:21:41,683 --> 00:21:43,563
Did you... Did you get into a fight?

373
00:21:43,643 --> 00:21:44,723
Why is there so much blood?

374
00:21:44,802 --> 00:21:45,802
I didn't fight.

375
00:21:47,082 --> 00:21:48,323
Just a small injury.

376
00:21:48,403 --> 00:21:50,049
A small injury? That's so much blood.

377
00:21:50,840 --> 00:21:51,840
Where's your outer robe?

378
00:21:53,282 --> 00:21:54,282
Outer robe?

379
00:21:56,322 --> 00:21:59,522
I left it in the study. It was too dirty.

380
00:21:59,603 --> 00:22:00,963
You can just throw it away for me.

381
00:22:01,683 --> 00:22:02,883
Still saying you didn't fight?

382
00:22:02,923 --> 00:22:04,809
Look, you've been scratched up!

383
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:06,778
Whose daughter did you harass this time?

384
00:22:06,802 --> 00:22:09,099
Finally ran into someone you shouldn't have messed with, huh?

385
00:22:09,123 --> 00:22:11,889
Can you stop making me sound like such a scumbag?

386
00:22:14,522 --> 00:22:16,443
I've got something good to show you.

387
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:19,480
- Open the door! Open it! - Where did I put it?

388
00:22:27,603 --> 00:22:29,208
Was anyone at your house last night?

389
00:22:37,883 --> 00:22:39,448
Where did those injuries come from?

390
00:22:41,722 --> 00:22:44,248
I got hurt while gathering herbs last night.

391
00:22:44,482 --> 00:22:46,329
Gathering herbs in the middle of the night?

392
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:48,102
Who are you trying to fool?

393
00:22:48,683 --> 00:22:50,939
Were you the one who killed the girl next door last night?

394
00:22:50,963 --> 00:22:51,963
What?

395
00:22:52,242 --> 00:22:54,906
- The girl next door? - Stop playing dumb! Did you kill her?

396
00:22:55,203 --> 00:22:57,242
Officer, there must be some mistake.

397
00:22:57,322 --> 00:22:59,265
Our young master would never kill anyone.

398
00:23:00,843 --> 00:23:03,243
We found the murder weapon, along with bloodstained clothes.

399
00:23:04,042 --> 00:23:05,146
What's going on here?

400
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:06,680
That's my...

401
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:09,400
That's my... On what grounds are you arresting him?

402
00:23:09,522 --> 00:23:10,682
You can't just take him away!

403
00:23:10,762 --> 00:23:11,762
Are you people...

404
00:23:13,883 --> 00:23:15,283
You can't arrest me!

405
00:23:15,363 --> 00:23:17,163
Do you have any evidence?

406
00:23:26,123 --> 00:23:27,123
Brother!

407
00:23:38,163 --> 00:23:39,528
The final verdict of the case

408
00:23:40,363 --> 00:23:43,443
was that my brother coveted the girl and tried to force himself on her.

409
00:23:43,883 --> 00:23:45,448
The girl resisted with all her might,

410
00:23:45,883 --> 00:23:47,443
and my brother accidentally killed her.

411
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:50,649
Had he and that girl had any prior encounters?

412
00:23:52,082 --> 00:23:53,963
I only saw them speak a few times.

413
00:23:54,443 --> 00:23:56,169
But Xu An testified that

414
00:23:56,603 --> 00:23:58,722
he'd seen my brother harassing her several times.

415
00:23:59,042 --> 00:24:00,288
Was he telling the truth?

416
00:24:01,403 --> 00:24:02,849
The girl was very beautiful.

417
00:24:03,403 --> 00:24:05,523
I did see my brother speaking flirtatiously before,

418
00:24:05,603 --> 00:24:06,785
trying to get close to her.

419
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:09,040
Memorize it.

420
00:24:18,562 --> 00:24:19,562
Miss,

421
00:24:19,923 --> 00:24:22,329
you just came back from outside the city, didn't you?

422
00:24:23,683 --> 00:24:24,683
How did you know?

423
00:24:29,562 --> 00:24:31,688
There's a flower caught in your hair.

424
00:24:32,042 --> 00:24:33,778
This kind of flower can be used as medicine.

425
00:24:33,802 --> 00:24:35,532
It only grows in the mountains outside the city.

426
00:24:35,556 --> 00:24:36,556
You know medicine?

427
00:24:37,443 --> 00:24:41,082
Of course. I was already treating patients when I was 16.

428
00:24:41,883 --> 00:24:43,728
I see you pass by here every day,

429
00:24:43,923 --> 00:24:45,169
always looking troubled.

430
00:24:45,883 --> 00:24:47,483
What's weighing so heavily on your mind?

431
00:24:50,042 --> 00:24:52,523
Miss, if you're in trouble, you have to tell me.

432
00:24:52,603 --> 00:24:54,538
Neighbors should help each other. No need to be shy.

433
00:24:54,562 --> 00:24:55,809
If you need anything...

434
00:24:57,403 --> 00:24:58,586
Just ask me.

435
00:24:59,603 --> 00:25:01,488
She's clearly not interested in talking to you.

436
00:25:01,883 --> 00:25:03,528
Just give it a rest.

437
00:25:04,522 --> 00:25:06,448
Can't you see how troubled she looks?

438
00:25:06,603 --> 00:25:08,379
She must be dealing with something difficult.

439
00:25:08,403 --> 00:25:10,513
Besides, we're neighbors.

440
00:25:10,736 --> 00:25:12,056
She's a young woman living alone.

441
00:25:12,482 --> 00:25:13,682
Shouldn't I show some concern?

442
00:25:13,963 --> 00:25:16,169
And if she looked ugly,

443
00:25:16,363 --> 00:25:17,809
would you still be this eager?

444
00:25:18,276 --> 00:25:20,962
There are ugly men in this world, but no ugly women.

445
00:25:21,282 --> 00:25:22,923
What would a kid like you know?

446
00:25:23,843 --> 00:25:25,163
Memorize your acupuncture charts.

447
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:27,626
It's the fastest way to learn.

448
00:25:30,363 --> 00:25:33,008
But that alone doesn't mean he would kill someone.

449
00:25:33,643 --> 00:25:35,683
What do you think, Zhan?

450
00:25:37,683 --> 00:25:40,203
You said they found the murder weapon, a dagger, in your house.

451
00:25:41,363 --> 00:25:43,000
If your brother was drunk

452
00:25:43,125 --> 00:25:44,619
and killed the girl next door in a moment of impulse,

453
00:25:44,643 --> 00:25:47,369
yet still remembered to bring the weapon back and hide it,

454
00:25:47,683 --> 00:25:50,083
then clearly he wasn't drunk enough to black out completely.

455
00:25:50,322 --> 00:25:52,724
If that's the case, he should've immediately cleaned off the blood,

456
00:25:52,748 --> 00:25:54,588
and disposed of the weapon and bloody clothes,

457
00:25:54,802 --> 00:25:57,329
not just lain on the bed and slept soundly.

458
00:25:58,683 --> 00:26:00,745
Yes, looking back now,

459
00:26:01,203 --> 00:26:02,723
there were so many suspicious details.

460
00:26:03,603 --> 00:26:04,928
Yet back then, I...

461
00:26:17,403 --> 00:26:19,426
Is this inner room the study?

462
00:27:05,522 --> 00:27:07,823
Bai, this book doesn't have a title.

463
00:27:08,042 --> 00:27:09,419
Could it be your brother's notebook?

464
00:27:09,443 --> 00:27:10,443
Don't read it!

465
00:27:11,002 --> 00:27:12,002
Why not?

466
00:27:24,963 --> 00:27:25,963
Uh...

467
00:27:26,082 --> 00:27:27,186
I'll wait for you outside.

468
00:27:33,082 --> 00:27:35,442
How could such book be left out in the open like that?

469
00:27:35,522 --> 00:27:37,409
My brother had several books like this.

470
00:27:37,643 --> 00:27:39,419
How would I know? I wasn't the one who left it there!

471
00:27:39,443 --> 00:27:40,443
Keep your voice down.

472
00:27:40,775 --> 00:27:41,953
Lady Huo might hear you.

473
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:44,826
With her hearing, she'll still hear me even if I whisper!

474
00:29:00,708 --> 00:29:01,970
There's so much blood here.

475
00:29:02,802 --> 00:29:04,849
That girl must've died in terrible pain.

476
00:29:06,002 --> 00:29:07,370
The authorities said they found traces

477
00:29:07,394 --> 00:29:08,819
of knockout incense outside the room.

478
00:29:08,843 --> 00:29:11,763
They said the girl woke up in the middle and resisted with all her might.

479
00:29:11,923 --> 00:29:14,323
My brother then slashed her until she was covered in wounds.

480
00:29:19,203 --> 00:29:20,803
Even rapists in the martial world rarely

481
00:29:20,867 --> 00:29:22,329
mess up when using knockout incense.

482
00:29:24,123 --> 00:29:25,728
Your family is a lineage of medicine.

483
00:29:25,963 --> 00:29:27,403
So how could he possibly fail at it?

484
00:29:32,082 --> 00:29:34,482
Officer Zhan!

485
00:29:35,322 --> 00:29:37,443
Come back with me now. We have to help Ming Zhu Er.

486
00:29:40,242 --> 00:29:42,609
You've only been at this manor a few years.

487
00:29:42,843 --> 00:29:43,962
If it weren't for me,

488
00:29:44,042 --> 00:29:46,208
would you know the true colors of those two brothers?

489
00:29:46,603 --> 00:29:50,008
His older brother committed murder.

490
00:29:50,963 --> 00:29:53,409
There used to be a maid in the manor named Mei.

491
00:29:53,802 --> 00:29:56,545
Jin Xue Wen chased after her every time he saw her.

492
00:29:56,643 --> 00:29:58,419
One moment calling her "beauty that could sink kingdoms,"

493
00:29:58,443 --> 00:30:00,099
the next comparing her to heavenly goddesses.

494
00:30:00,123 --> 00:30:03,586
He praised her like she was some celestial maiden from the moon palace.

495
00:30:03,802 --> 00:30:05,603
Mei wanted nothing to do with him.

496
00:30:05,683 --> 00:30:08,402
He even tried getting handsy and touching her hair.

497
00:30:08,482 --> 00:30:10,409
After touching it, he'd smell his hand.

498
00:30:12,643 --> 00:30:14,003
Mei was terrified out of her mind.

499
00:30:14,082 --> 00:30:16,169
A few months later, she quit and went home.

500
00:30:16,883 --> 00:30:18,528
That's the kind of person he was.

501
00:30:18,802 --> 00:30:21,248
How could the authorities possibly have wronged him?

502
00:30:21,562 --> 00:30:23,042
And then there's his younger brother,

503
00:30:23,562 --> 00:30:25,202
just some drifter from the martial world.

504
00:30:25,282 --> 00:30:26,426
What wouldn't he do?

505
00:30:26,683 --> 00:30:28,483
He's capable of all sorts of terrible things.

506
00:30:30,722 --> 00:30:32,213
Look at his servant boy,

507
00:30:32,280 --> 00:30:35,365
a sneaky little mongrel who steals and cheats.

508
00:30:38,082 --> 00:30:39,323
How dare you glare at me!

509
00:30:39,403 --> 00:30:41,500
I'll smash your eyes!

510
00:30:44,082 --> 00:30:45,082
Young Master!

511
00:30:47,163 --> 00:30:49,522
What is this? What are you trying to do?

512
00:30:53,242 --> 00:30:54,773
Are you alright? Are you hurt?

513
00:30:54,840 --> 00:30:56,720
Don't worry, Young Master. Not a scratch on me.

514
00:30:56,883 --> 00:30:59,282
That old man framed me. I didn't steal anything.

515
00:30:59,403 --> 00:31:00,545
Framed you?

516
00:31:00,883 --> 00:31:03,323
I caught you red-handed, and you still dare deny it?

517
00:31:03,403 --> 00:31:04,928
You said you caught him red-handed.

518
00:31:05,282 --> 00:31:07,386
Then where's the stolen item? Did you find it?

519
00:31:08,082 --> 00:31:11,123
He was skulking around the library,

520
00:31:11,203 --> 00:31:12,939
clearly trying to sneak in and steal something!

521
00:31:12,963 --> 00:31:15,496
- But I didn't go inside. - Since you insist he stole something,

522
00:31:15,520 --> 00:31:17,840
then let's go to the authorities and settle this properly.

523
00:31:18,082 --> 00:31:20,218
Filing a false accusation means taking some lashes, you know.

524
00:31:20,242 --> 00:31:21,242
You...

525
00:31:23,722 --> 00:31:25,288
You injured my hand.

526
00:31:26,002 --> 00:31:27,025
It hurts!

527
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:29,216
I can't move it. I can't be bothered arguing with you anymore.

528
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:31,698
Young Master, Jin Zhen Ping has been in that room for a long time.

529
00:31:31,722 --> 00:31:33,802
Something feels wrong. We should go check on him.

530
00:31:36,002 --> 00:31:37,002
Where are you going?

531
00:31:37,683 --> 00:31:39,528
What, do you want a few more?

532
00:31:40,883 --> 00:31:43,688
Fine. Fine. Just you wait.

533
00:31:45,322 --> 00:31:47,322
Break it up! Everyone, get lost!

534
00:31:48,403 --> 00:31:50,688
From now on, none of you are allowed near Jujing Hall.

535
00:31:51,082 --> 00:31:53,083
And if anyone dares talk to them,

536
00:31:53,163 --> 00:31:54,720
I'll break their legs!

537
00:32:12,722 --> 00:32:15,248
You caused such a huge scene in front of Qinghui Hall,

538
00:32:15,843 --> 00:32:18,208
and now everyone in my residence is gossiping nonstop.

539
00:32:19,002 --> 00:32:21,889
So I had Mr. Xu tell them a few stories

540
00:32:22,322 --> 00:32:23,688
to let everyone know

541
00:32:24,242 --> 00:32:26,293
what kind of person Jin Xue Wen really was.

542
00:32:26,468 --> 00:32:28,229
Since you've thrown your dignity away,

543
00:32:28,320 --> 00:32:29,440
then stay here all you want.

544
00:32:30,002 --> 00:32:31,002
Keep searching.

545
00:32:31,242 --> 00:32:32,569
Search for what you came to find.

546
00:32:39,923 --> 00:32:41,856
Just now, I was sorting through

547
00:32:42,055 --> 00:32:44,666
some old prescriptions gathering dust in the corner.

548
00:32:46,203 --> 00:32:48,569
That's when I remembered a patient I once treated.

549
00:32:49,722 --> 00:32:51,609
He was also from the martial world,

550
00:32:51,923 --> 00:32:53,883
and he had also been poisoned with Nightmare Sky.

551
00:32:54,643 --> 00:32:56,053
I remember it clearly,

552
00:32:56,195 --> 00:32:57,395
during the entire day,

553
00:32:57,480 --> 00:33:00,983
he was lucid for no more than an hour.

554
00:33:01,722 --> 00:33:06,186
The rest of the time, he was trapped in endless hallucinations.

555
00:33:06,963 --> 00:33:09,129
In the end, consumed by those hallucinations,

556
00:33:09,683 --> 00:33:10,866
he took his own life.

557
00:33:14,603 --> 00:33:15,919
He was treated too late.

558
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:17,360
Medicine could no longer save him.

559
00:33:17,643 --> 00:33:19,369
That's how he ended up that way.

560
00:33:21,163 --> 00:33:23,800
Your two sworn brothers won't end up like him too, will they?

561
00:33:24,155 --> 00:33:25,475
How long have they been poisoned?

562
00:33:25,843 --> 00:33:27,025
Hand over the antidote!

563
00:33:27,522 --> 00:33:28,522
If you kill me,

564
00:33:28,963 --> 00:33:32,049
you'll be sending your sworn brothers to their deaths.

565
00:33:32,843 --> 00:33:34,129
Just like 15 years ago,

566
00:33:34,562 --> 00:33:37,443
when you personally sealed your brother's fate.

567
00:33:41,722 --> 00:33:45,008
You've taken them to the old house several times now.

568
00:33:46,163 --> 00:33:47,448
Found anything yet?

569
00:33:50,883 --> 00:33:53,208
Your brother's bones have long since turned to dust.

570
00:33:54,482 --> 00:33:56,202
Only now you think of overturning his case?

571
00:33:56,242 --> 00:33:57,849
Isn't it a little too late for that?

572
00:34:00,843 --> 00:34:03,253
From the interrogation to the final verdict back then,

573
00:34:03,376 --> 00:34:04,901
you never showed up once.

574
00:34:05,522 --> 00:34:08,169
I'd say you condemned your brother to death

575
00:34:08,522 --> 00:34:11,089
even earlier than the magistrate did.

576
00:34:15,282 --> 00:34:16,939
You really can't judge a person by appearances.

577
00:34:16,963 --> 00:34:19,106
Look what he did to a decent young woman.

578
00:34:19,282 --> 00:34:22,499
Even dying in prison wouldn't be enough to satisfy the outrage.

579
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:24,339
The younger one doesn't seem to be up to any good either.

580
00:34:24,363 --> 00:34:26,160
Bet he's just like his brother.

581
00:34:26,241 --> 00:34:28,320
- Definitely the same. - Exactly.

582
00:34:28,403 --> 00:34:29,403
Pervert!

583
00:34:29,522 --> 00:34:31,443
Hit him!

584
00:34:32,643 --> 00:34:34,162
- Hit him! - Alright, enough!

585
00:34:34,242 --> 00:34:36,402
Hey, hey! What are you doing? Back off! Go away!

586
00:34:36,482 --> 00:34:38,883
Go on, get out of here!

587
00:34:49,603 --> 00:34:52,968
Your brother's funeral arrangements are mostly settled now.

588
00:34:54,722 --> 00:34:56,540
I had someone draft a petition.

589
00:34:56,668 --> 00:34:57,908
See if it looks alright to you.

590
00:34:58,363 --> 00:35:00,083
I was going to ask the Jin family about it,

591
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:02,927
but every last one of them avoided me.

592
00:35:03,363 --> 00:35:06,923
Damn them all. They don't care about family ties one bit anymore.

593
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,767
I must be getting senile.

594
00:35:11,848 --> 00:35:13,071
You're still so young,

595
00:35:13,802 --> 00:35:15,522
how could you possibly understand all this?

596
00:35:16,322 --> 00:35:18,719
In a couple of days, we'll set off

597
00:35:19,216 --> 00:35:21,056
and appeal our case at the prefectural office.

598
00:35:24,002 --> 00:35:25,002
You don't want to go?

599
00:35:26,123 --> 00:35:27,889
You don't believe Ninth was wrongly accused?

600
00:35:29,002 --> 00:35:30,722
Ninth may not have had the best reputation,

601
00:35:30,963 --> 00:35:32,809
but there's no way he could have done

602
00:35:32,963 --> 00:35:34,528
something as heinous as that.

603
00:35:48,723 --> 00:35:50,509
You didn't even believe your own brother.

604
00:35:50,615 --> 00:35:52,135
Why should the rest of us believe him?

605
00:35:52,600 --> 00:35:54,043
And you want to hold Jin family accountable?

606
00:35:54,067 --> 00:35:55,187
Do you really think you can?

607
00:35:55,923 --> 00:35:58,443
The person who owed Jin Xue Wen the most wasn't anyone else,

608
00:35:59,002 --> 00:36:00,002
it was you.

609
00:36:00,923 --> 00:36:01,946
Jin Yue Wen.

610
00:36:02,723 --> 00:36:04,299
If the case truly was a miscarriage of justice,

611
00:36:04,323 --> 00:36:06,643
then the ones who wronged his brother were the real killer

612
00:36:06,723 --> 00:36:08,859
and the corrupt officials who condemned an innocent man.

613
00:36:08,883 --> 00:36:11,169
You can't blame a ten-year-old child.

614
00:36:11,250 --> 00:36:14,769
So being young is enough to excuse him now?

615
00:36:15,122 --> 00:36:17,946
I remember very clearly that ten-year-old child

616
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:20,241
kneeling outside the gates of the Jin Residence,

617
00:36:20,322 --> 00:36:22,608
begging in the pouring rain for Naiheyin Pill.

618
00:36:24,202 --> 00:36:25,644
I find it hard to believe that he was

619
00:36:25,668 --> 00:36:27,379
actually concerned about his brother's life

620
00:36:27,403 --> 00:36:29,848
when Jin Xue Wen was dying.

621
00:36:30,923 --> 00:36:33,323
It was probably to keep people from pointing fingers at him.

622
00:36:33,363 --> 00:36:34,425
It was all an act.

623
00:36:35,002 --> 00:36:37,408
And because of it, he won Fourth Aunt's sympathy.

624
00:36:37,803 --> 00:36:39,403
She wanted to keep him in the residence,

625
00:36:39,642 --> 00:36:40,666
to raise him herself.

626
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:44,640
Bai Yu Tang, what a clever move, killing two birds with one stone.

627
00:36:44,682 --> 00:36:45,682
Shut up!

628
00:36:46,642 --> 00:36:47,865
If you say another word,

629
00:36:48,323 --> 00:36:50,009
I'll teach you a lesson for Bai!

630
00:36:54,363 --> 00:36:55,888
You want to be friends with him?

631
00:36:57,763 --> 00:36:58,763
Does he deserve it?

632
00:36:58,883 --> 00:37:00,853
A man who couldn't even trust his own brother,

633
00:37:01,061 --> 00:37:02,508
would he ever truly be your friend?

634
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:12,926
I'd like to be alone.

635
00:37:36,963 --> 00:37:38,248
Let's go see Fourth Madam.

636
00:37:41,522 --> 00:37:42,762
You'll return to the inn first.

637
00:37:47,162 --> 00:37:48,162
Fourth Madam,

638
00:37:48,323 --> 00:37:51,084
has there been any progress regarding the antidote for Nightmare Sky?

639
00:37:54,122 --> 00:37:56,848
I'm afraid there's not much I can do to help you.

640
00:37:57,883 --> 00:38:01,002
I heard Little Seventeenth and Third had another huge fight today.

641
00:38:01,376 --> 00:38:02,616
I'll try to talk to him again.

642
00:38:02,723 --> 00:38:03,723
Fourth Madam,

643
00:38:03,883 --> 00:38:05,449
what Bai needs is the antidote,

644
00:38:05,763 --> 00:38:07,009
not comforting words.

645
00:38:11,323 --> 00:38:13,129
You once saved Zhan's life.

646
00:38:13,682 --> 00:38:15,374
And Bai has always been deeply grateful

647
00:38:15,454 --> 00:38:17,214
for how you cared for him when he was young.

648
00:38:18,522 --> 00:38:21,082
They can't speak harshly to you, so I will.

649
00:38:22,522 --> 00:38:23,848
After the shipwreck back then,

650
00:38:24,522 --> 00:38:26,728
why didn't the Jin family continue searching for Bai?

651
00:38:27,202 --> 00:38:29,283
Could it be you were all hoping he'd die out there?

652
00:38:29,522 --> 00:38:31,785
No, of course not.

653
00:38:32,243 --> 00:38:33,813
Whether intentional or not,

654
00:38:33,988 --> 00:38:35,948
the Jin family left him to fend for himself.

655
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:37,367
You owe him for that.

656
00:38:38,482 --> 00:38:41,002
Shouldn't you be doing everything you can to make it up to him?

657
00:38:48,002 --> 00:38:49,408
When Bai came to your door,

658
00:38:50,122 --> 00:38:51,893
he didn't ask for anything unreasonable.

659
00:38:52,060 --> 00:38:54,808
He only asked the Jin family to save his sworn brothers.

660
00:38:55,642 --> 00:38:58,225
Jin Zhen Ping has the antidote, but he refuses to save them.

661
00:38:58,803 --> 00:39:01,649
And the Jin family elders are turning a blind eye to it.

662
00:39:02,323 --> 00:39:04,208
Is this how a respected medical family

663
00:39:04,602 --> 00:39:06,848
always treats people whose lives are at stake?

664
00:39:07,883 --> 00:39:09,523
Or is it simply because he's Bai Yu Tang?

665
00:39:11,682 --> 00:39:14,529
You once asked whether Bai Yu Tang had suffered a lot out there.

666
00:39:15,323 --> 00:39:17,803
He told you it was all in the past.

667
00:39:18,642 --> 00:39:20,049
But have you ever thought about

668
00:39:20,482 --> 00:39:23,265
what a ten-year-old child wandering the martial world alone

669
00:39:23,763 --> 00:39:25,609
would have had to endure just to survive?

670
00:39:26,482 --> 00:39:29,288
He never spoke of those things because he didn't want to upset you.

671
00:39:29,520 --> 00:39:31,058
He's worried sick about his sworn brothers,

672
00:39:31,082 --> 00:39:33,353
yet he wouldn't pressure you for the antidote

673
00:39:33,561 --> 00:39:35,881
because he didn't want to put you in a difficult position.

674
00:39:35,923 --> 00:39:36,923
I...

675
00:39:49,976 --> 00:39:51,616
Why do you keep looking around like that?

676
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:56,560
Steward Xu said Bai Yu Tang is capable of murder and arson,

677
00:39:56,640 --> 00:39:57,640
that he'd do anything.

678
00:39:57,803 --> 00:39:59,953
You humiliated him so badly in public,

679
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:02,841
so wouldn't someone like him try to ambush and retaliate against you?

680
00:40:03,122 --> 00:40:06,208
Yet you still chose such a remote road to make house calls.

681
00:40:08,042 --> 00:40:09,728
It's broad daylight.

682
00:40:10,482 --> 00:40:12,368
If he dares to come, then let him come.

683
00:40:13,723 --> 00:40:15,883
In fact, I'll think less of him if he doesn't show up.

684
00:40:16,803 --> 00:40:18,203
Isn't he after the antidote?

685
00:40:18,283 --> 00:40:20,688
Doesn't he want revenge on Jin family for Jin Xue Wen?

686
00:40:21,122 --> 00:40:22,122
Let him come.

687
00:40:22,323 --> 00:40:24,825
Don't just run your mouth and put on an act!

688
00:41:07,363 --> 00:41:08,363
Master.

689
00:41:09,055 --> 00:41:10,055
I'm so exhausted.

690
00:41:10,562 --> 00:41:11,848
Why did you walk so fast?

691
00:41:14,763 --> 00:41:17,283
Alright, alright. I wasn't trying to kill him.

692
00:41:17,363 --> 00:41:19,203
I know how Jin Zhen Ping operates.

693
00:41:19,283 --> 00:41:21,683
Those prescriptions in the library are his life's work.

694
00:41:21,763 --> 00:41:23,009
He'd never actually burn them.

695
00:41:23,443 --> 00:41:26,220
I'm following him to see his next move

696
00:41:26,422 --> 00:41:27,869
and find the formulas he hid away.

697
00:41:28,723 --> 00:41:29,969
But did you ever consider

698
00:41:30,682 --> 00:41:33,466
that they only let you follow because they had already set a trap?

699
00:41:34,082 --> 00:41:35,980
I noticed those people tailing us.

700
00:41:36,140 --> 00:41:38,340
- The Tang Sect members... - Weren't a match for you.

701
00:41:39,682 --> 00:41:41,848
Alright. Stop wasting time on Jin Zhen Ping.

702
00:41:42,723 --> 00:41:44,602
We got the antidote formula.

703
00:41:48,923 --> 00:41:50,522
I've sent someone to deliver

704
00:41:50,600 --> 00:41:52,706
a copy of the formula to Xiankong Island right away.

705
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:54,096
Where did this formula come from?

706
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:55,200
Fourth Madam gave it to us.

707
00:41:55,443 --> 00:41:57,666
You should thank Lady Huo for this.

708
00:41:58,122 --> 00:41:59,609
She convinced Fourth Aunt?

709
00:42:01,923 --> 00:42:03,696
When Fourth Madam sent someone to give it to us,

710
00:42:03,720 --> 00:42:06,216
she said she figured it out herself after studying ancient texts.

711
00:42:06,240 --> 00:42:08,320
She claimed it had nothing to do with Jin Zhen Ping.

712
00:42:09,082 --> 00:42:11,728
In the end, she's still protecting him.

713
00:42:12,202 --> 00:42:14,409
Never mind. What matters is that we've gotten the formula.

714
00:42:14,433 --> 00:42:15,939
I need to go thank Lady Huo right away.

715
00:42:15,963 --> 00:42:16,963
Not just her.

716
00:42:17,082 --> 00:42:19,963
Ming Zhu Er is still upset about being falsely accused earlier.

717
00:42:20,363 --> 00:42:23,420
You didn't forget that you promised to make it up to him, did you?

718
00:42:23,553 --> 00:42:24,736
Why didn't you remind me sooner?

719
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,479
At least I could've brought him something.

720
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:27,640
Now I'm going empty-handed.

721
00:42:27,843 --> 00:42:28,843
Too late for that.

722
00:42:28,963 --> 00:42:30,963
Ming Zhu Er's been by my side since he was little.

723
00:42:31,082 --> 00:42:33,529
I've never seen him suffer such humiliation before.

724
00:42:34,162 --> 00:42:35,162
Go check on him quickly.

725
00:42:35,642 --> 00:42:36,642
Come with me.

726
00:42:44,082 --> 00:42:45,082
Grilled fish?

727
00:42:46,154 --> 00:42:47,640
Quite a nose you've got.

728
00:42:49,466 --> 00:42:53,120
White Rat, come over here. This fish is for you. You grill it.

729
00:42:53,585 --> 00:42:54,585
What a feast.

730
00:43:03,883 --> 00:43:06,728
Huo Xiao Mei, how exactly did you convince Fourth Aunt?
